Parliament, Tuesday, 23 October 2018 – The Portfolio Committee on Public Enterprises will tomorrow meet to consider the first draft of the Eskom inquiry report. The meeting will be closed to members of the media and the public. Subsequently, the committee will brief the media on its discussions. Details of the meeting: Date: Wednesday, 24 October 2018
	Time: 09:30 am
	Venue: Committee Room 3, Upper Ground Floor, 90 Plein Building Meanwhile, the Portfolio Committee on Energy will continue its public hearings on the draft Integrated Resource Plan 2018 (IRP). Details of the public hearing: Date: Wednesday, 24 October 2018
	Time: 10:00 am
	Venue: Committee Room V454, 4th Floor, Old Assembly Building ISSUED BY THE PARLIAMENTARY COMMUNICATION SERVICES For media enquiries or interviews with the Chairperson, please contact the committee’s Media Officer: Name: Ms Yoliswa Landu
	Parliamentary Communication Services
	Tel: 021 403 8203 
	Cell: 081 497 4694
